Package no.kartverket.geopose Description

This package contains everything needed to maintain a transformation between the Tango coordinate system and a geographical coordinate system. The main access point to this package is the abstract class PositionOrientationProvider with its specific realization: ARPoseProvider. The package requires the Efficient java matrix Library (ejml), currently of version 0.31.
